5.18.20  11:07 am   How do you write a good bass line that fits with the contours of the vocals. Do you ever match the vocals in unison/octave with bass lines or do you always harmonize with the vocal line instead?

     usually neither

     I had someone tel me one time that when you play bass in octave/unison with the vocal melody or any other melody for that matter, it weakens the melody, do you feel that's true?

     if someone told you, it doesn't count. the only way you will know is when you start trying it. It's like carrying someone over complicated terrain. who can possibly explain to you where to put your feet?
